Collaborative Forecasts

You can review forecast rollups by team, then by forecast group or product family, or by group or product family, then by team.

View Forecasts Grouped How It Makes Sense to You

Review forecast rollups by team, forecast group, or product family on the forecasts page. For user role hierarchy forecast types that include groups or product families, Sales Managers can select to view forecasts rolled up by team, then by product family or group. Or, they can select to view forecasts rolled up by group values or product family, then by team.

Further Customize the Forecast Guidance You Receive in Copilot

The Get Forecast Guidance copilot action is now powered by a flow that customers can modify to better define copilot's response around forecasting. In Flow Builder, modify risk criteria, the number of opportunities to display, gap-to-quota formulas, and other elements to get the most out of forecast guidance in copilot.
